---
title: Cal Smart Ginger Miso-Glazed Tilapia with Ginger-Garlic Veggies
description: Miso adds savoury umami flavour to any dish! Combined with butter, soy sauce and honey, it becomes an irresistible glaze. Veggies tossed with ginger and garlic further complement this union of flavours!
